            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Victoria</abbr><ex>e</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Vesomn</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Sever</abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> o<supplied reason="lost">p</supplied>&amp;lt;t=I&amp;gt;(io) <lb n="4"/>&amp;lt;l=T&amp;gt;(egionis) <surplus>A</surplus>I <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>inerviae</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): CIL 12, 00077: Z. 1: Victoria; Z. 3: oi; Z. 4: taim. Hirschfeld in CIL 12, 00077: Z. 2: Ve[s]son(ius); Z. 4: [l(egionis)] I M(inerviae); Mommsen in CIL 12, 00077: Z. 3: S. [f. Q]u[i]r. O[p]ta[tus]; Ganet: da CIL con imprecisioni nella trascrizione del testo; Morabito: Z. 3-4: op/t(io) &amp;lt;l=A&amp;gt;(egionis). L´attribuzione del documento alle &amp;quot;&amp;quot;Alpes Cottiae&amp;quot;&amp;quot; in base a CIL 05, 810; cfr. A.L.F. Rivet, Gallia Narbonensis with a chapter on Alpes Maritimae (London 1988) 338; P. Arnaud, Un flaminat provincial des Alpes-Maritimes à Embrun. Flaminat provincial, incolatus et frontière des Alpes-Maritimes, RAN 32, 1999, 47-48; E. Cimarosti, Le iscrizioni di età romana sul versante italiano delle Alpes Cottiae (Barcelona 2012), 61; &amp;quot;&amp;quot;contra&amp;quot;&amp;quot; S. Morabito, Inscriptions latines des Alpes Maritimes (Nice-Montpellier 2010) 34-35.</p>
            </div>
